  <title class="- topic/title ">Save Your Campaign</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">When you have finished setting your
	 campaign parameters, save the campaign. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
    <context id="context_27ABB743E59949EDBA4064FBE1B6019A" class="- topic/section task/context ">
      <p class="- topic/p ">You have two options: 
		</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
        <ul id="ul_C2D0123CE0F24056B7F9A96ED1688259" class="- topic/ul ">
          <li id="li_DD2F3B910548466598CA5272F52804B7" class="- topic/li ">
            <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Save and
				Approve</uicontrol> saves the campaign and activates it. 
		  </li>
          <li id="li_F1EE45A4FC8542BBBE42740B86E391E2" class="- topic/li ">
            <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Save</uicontrol> saves
			 the campaign without making it active. 
		  </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </context>
